20created%20in%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fecon%2Fcurrentdata%2F%3FprogramCode%3DBFS%26startYear%3D2004%26endYear%3D2024%26categories%5B%5D%3DTOTAL%26dataType%3DBA_BA%26geoLevel%3DUS%26adjusted%3D1%26notAdjusted%3D1%26errorData%3D0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20data%20from%20the%20United%20States%20Census%20Bureau.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Within%2010%20years%2C%20more%20than%2065%25%20of%20them%20will%20fail%2C%20the%20USCB's%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20seasoned%20entrepreneurs%20will%20tell%20you%20that%20failure%20is%20part%20of%20success.%20True%20visionaries%20pick%20themselves%20up%20and%20turn%20to%20their%20next%20innovation%2C%20ready%20to%20once%20again%20confront%20the%20question%3A%20What's%20the%20secret%20to%20a%20winning%20startup%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteve%20Blank%20is%20the%20man%20who%20has%20provided%20that%20answer%20for%20many%20founders.%20After%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20involved%20in%20eight%20technology%20startups%2C%20half%20of%20which%20reached%20IPO%2C%20Blank%20turned%20to%20academia%20and%20developed%20a%20method%20for%20leading%20early-stage%20companies%20to%20success%20%E2%80%94%20the%20lean%20startup%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lean%20startup%2C%20as%20Blank%20explained%20in%20a%202013%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhbr.org%2F2013%2F05%2Fwhy-the-lean-start-up-changes-everything%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Business%20Review%3C%2Fa%3E%20cover%20story%2C%20favors%20experimentation%2C%20a%20customer-centric%20approach%2C%20and%20agility%20over%20traditional%20up%20front%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20the%20method%20was%20the%20recognition%20that%20early-stage%20companies%20couldn't%20and%20shouldn't%20aim%20to%20operate%20like%20large%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20become%20the%20go-to%20template%20for%20startups%2C%20is%20taught%20in%20business%20schools%20worldwide%2C%20informs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fedtech.io%2Fresource%2Fhow-lean-start-up-methodology-can-benefit-va-innovators%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20commerce%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20has%20earned%20Blank%20unofficial%20status%20as%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.ox.ac.uk%2Fnews%2Fai-will-reinvent-every-piece-commerce-and-enterprise-next-year-says-father-modern-entrepreneurship-steve-blank%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFather%20of%20Modern%20Entrepreneurship%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20his%20work%20as%20an%20adjunct%20professor%20at%20Stanford%2C%20Blank%20is%20involved%20in%20efforts%20to%20imbue%20US%20national%20security%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20entrepreneurship%20he's%20renowned%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20world%20enters%20what%20Blank%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bbeginning%20of%20massive%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20the%20legendary%20entrepreneur%20about%20what%20he'd%20do%20if%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20grow%20a%20business%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20biggest%20piece%20of%20advice%3F%20Have%20fun%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20not%20playing%20with%20all%20the%20tools%20and%20trying%20to%20build%20apps%20on%20top%20of%20them%2C%20you're%20already%20obsolete%2C%26quot%3B%20Blank%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIn%20twenty%20years%2C%20it%20will%20be%20the%20companies%20with%20AI%20in%20their%20DNA%20that%20are%20thriving.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEntrepreneurs%20should%20immerse%20themselves%20in%20this%20rapidly%20changing%20environment.%20If%20they%20don't%20they'll%20be%20left%20behind%20by%20the%20new%20wave%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20veteran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20your%20experiments%20are%20not%20making%20you%20giggle%2C%20you're%20not%20experimenting%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Steve%20Blank%20sits%20on%20a%20stage%20with%20a%20mic%2C%20holding%20his%20hand%20outreached%20to%20the%20audience.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f2c4a58a6f0e13d294a5464%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlank's%20methodology%20can%20only%20be%20enhanced%20by%20AI%2C%20he%20told%20BI.%20%3Cp%3ESteve%20Blank%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20applies%20to%20his%20own%20methodology%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20was%20still%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20I%20would%20immediately%20be%20AI-enabling%20that%20whole%20lean%20startup%20model%20and%20building%20enterprise%20software%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Blank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pieces%20of%20the%20lean%20startup%20are%20just%20so%20obvious%20to%20me%20to%20be%20automated%20and%20then%20strung%20together.%20That%20doesn't%20replace%20my%20process%2C%20it%20augments%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoing%20it%20manually%20will%20look%20silly%20in%20another%20five%20or%2010%20years%2C%20if%20not%20sooner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlank%20acknowledged%20there%20are%20risks%20and%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-disruption-ai-future-careers-blue-collar-desk-work-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20industries%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20devastated%26quot%3B%20by%20AI.%20But%20he%20said%20the%20people%20claiming%20the%20technology%20will%20end%20the%20world%20are%20fooling%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20there%20aren't%20mistakes%20to%20be%20made.%20The%20most%20common%20issue%20for%20innovators%20right%20now%20is%20that%20they're%20putting%20too%20much%20trust%20in%20AI%20working%20consistently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20works%20until%20it%20doesn't.%20But%20then%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20won't%20tell%20you%20when%20it's%20not%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20Blank%20told%20BI.%20An%20outlandish%20answer%20on%20a%20chatbot%20may%20be%20a%20small%20issue%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20designing%20an%20aircraft%20wing%20using%20AI-enabled%20computation%2C%20those%20calculations%20are%20mission-critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20the%20interesting%20thing%20about%20a%20neural%20net%3B%20you%20really%20don't%20know%20how%20it's%20coming%20up%20with%20its%20answer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasing%20references%20or%20ways%20to%20check%20how%20LLMs%20have%20come%20up%20with%20their%20outcomes%20will%20be%20crucial%20to%20solving%20this%20problem%20going%20forward%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20Blank's%20perspective%2C%20one%20side%20of%20entrepreneurship%20that%20is%20safe%20in%20the%20emerging%20AI%20world%20is%20the%20role%20of%20the%20visionary%20founder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20passionate%20set%20of%20founders%20who%20see%20over%20the%20horizon%20and%20see%20something%20that%20no%20one%20else%20does%2C%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20with%20us%20forever.%20All%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20different%20is%20the%20tools%20and%20the%20markets%20that%20they%20go%20after.%20Founders%20are%20closer%20to%20artists%20than%20any%20other%20profession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20resilient%2C%20and%20they're%20driven%20by%20a%20passion%20for%20creation%20that%20is%20never%20going%20to%20go%20away%20as%20long%20as%20human%20beings%20are%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-blank-lean-startup-method-advice-for-founders-ai-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721641668000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66953aa95439fb59cebd5a50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-blank-lean-startup-method-advice-for-founders-ai-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Legendary%20entrepreneur%20Steve%20Blank%20said%20entrepreneurs%20are%20making%20one%20big%20mistake%20when%20i