0financiers%20raked%20in%20millions%2C%20these%20lawsuits%20allege.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20dozen%20of%20these%20lawsuits%20were%20filed%20in%20the%20past%20month%20alone%2C%20and%20many%20more%20may%20be%20on%20the%20way.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20the%20process%20of%20filing%20cases%20on%20behalf%20of%20approximately%20250%20victims%2C%20with%20more%20reaching%20out%20weekly%2C%26quot%3B%20Bowe%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20scope%20of%20this%20litigation%20tsunami%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20in%20California%20used%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3Btens%20of%20thousands%20of%20children%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20November%20order%20granting%20class%20certification%20to%20one%20of%20at%20least%20two%20class-action%20trafficking%20suits%20against%20Pornhub%20and%20MindGeek%2C%20which%20rebranded%20last%20year%20as%20Aylo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20evidence%20from%20the%20defendants'%20own%20records%20demonstrating%20the%20presence%20of%20thousands%20of%20pieces%20of%20CSAM%20on%20their%20sites%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20previous%20years%2C%20US%20District%20Judge%20Cormac%20J.%20Carney%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24888992-mindgeek-class-cert-order%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20the%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%20the%20acronym%20for%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221194%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20excerpt%20from%20a%20California%20federal%20judge's%20November%20order%20granting%20class-action%20status%20to%20one%20of%20dozens%20of%20Pornhub%20lawsuits.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669b4d8849138fa6f6e41158%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20excerpt%20from%20a%20federal%20judge's%20November%20order%20granting%20class-action%20status%20to%20one%20of%20dozens%20of%20Pornhub%20lawsuits.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch