%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20doubly%20more%20sensitive%20when%20you're%20dealing%20with%20adult%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStabile%20added%20that%20if%20Mickelwait%20finds%20something%20of%20concern%2C%20she%20should%20report%20it.%26quot%3BHistorically%2C%20what%20Laila%20has%20done%20is%20air%20it%20through%20the%20press%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMickelwait%20said%20that%20she%20has%20reported%20many%20hundreds%20of%20videos%20to%20law%20enforcement%20and%20anti-trafficking%20watchdogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20recently%2C%20she%20said%2C%20she%20reported%20to%20state%20authorities%20the%20Pornhub%20video%20showing%20a%20woman%20shouting%20in%20pain%20and%20asking%20not%20to%20be%20filmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20critical%20to%20bring%20justice%20to%20these%20victims%2C%20but%20also%20to%20be%20a%20deterrent%20to%20future%20abusers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BPornhub%2C%20to%20this%20day%2C%20is%20still%20a%20crime%20scene%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20shut%20down%20and%20its%20owners%20held%20accountable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpornhub-is-awash-in-lawsuits-unverified-videos-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721640602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66995e1249138fa6f6e39284%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpornhub-is-awash-in-lawsuits-unverified-videos-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20300%20plaintiffs%20say%20Pornhub%20profited%20from%20their%20assaults.%20An%20anti-trafficking%20advocate%20says%20there%20will%20be%20more%20legal%20challenges%20to%20come.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpornhub-is-awash-in-lawsuits-unverified-videos-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%2