e%2C%20government%2C%20and%20international%20relations.%20After%20graduate%20school%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20an%20economics%20editor%20in%20Boston%20before%20pivoting%20to%20banking%2C%20where%20I%20stayed%20for%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20in%201980%20and%20took%20a%20job%20in%20corporate%20development%20before%20moving%20to%20theater%20and%20documentary%20production%2C%20where%20my%20strength%20was%20raising%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I'm%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-ghostwriter-silicon-valley-vc-venture-founder-san-francisco-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eghostwriter%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20celebrities%20and%20leaders%20in%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22450f9594-2e50-412e-b065-70c2cc75da14%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20wrote%20my%20mom's%20life%20story%20first%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20was%20an%20opera%20singer%2C%20and%20I%20wrote%20a%20book%20about%20her%20life%20for%20her.%20She%20got%20so%20much%20pleasure%20from%20it%2C%20and%20I%20did%2C%20too.%20I%20didn't%20even%20know%20what%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-pr-firms-are-making-linkedin-ghostwriting-a-big-business-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eghostwriter%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20or%20if%20there%20was%20a%20business%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20some%20of%20my%20biggest%20donors%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20try%20something%20completely%20different.%20Some%20of%20them%20became%20my%20first%20ghostwriting%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228dfb946b-36eb-4abc-96e5-a2b85f012eac%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20my%20company%2C%20Write%20Wisdom%2C%20in%202007%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20seven%20writers%20who%20work%20for%20me%20on%20a%20per-book%20basis.%20I%20negotiate%20the%20fees%2C%20collect%20payments%2C%20and%20distribute%20payments%20to%20our%20writers.%20The%20writers%20set%20the%20interview%20an