0my%20name.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20however%2C%20my%20name%20isn't%20on%20the%20cover.%20The%20wording%20is%20usually%20%26quot%3Bwith%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20%26quot%3Band%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20story%20is%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7ce0b4d-e73c-40fc-b252-05bb99bb1bcd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20do%2010%20two-hour%20interviews%20with%20our%20client%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interviews%20are%20recorded%20and%20transcribed%20and%20become%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20first%20draft.%20Part%20of%20the%20writing%20also%20includes%20research%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-chatbots-fact-checking-prompts-made-up-answers-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efact-checking%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20a%20collaborative%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20client%20looks%20at%20the%20first%20draft%2C%20it%20often%20prompts%20them%20to%20think%20of%20things%20they've%20forgotten.%20We%20do%20further%20interviews%20and%20incorporate%20that%20material%20into%20the%20book.%20After%20that%2C%20we%20do%20another%20edit%2C%20which%20is%20more%20of%20a%20polish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manuscript%20should%20typically%20be%20completed%20in%20about%20a%20year.%20Working%20with%20successful%20people%20usually%20means%20they're%20extremely%20busy%2C%20so%20sometimes%20we%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20them%20to%20find%20time%20for%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f32dd7a9-7551-44db-bc63-c6054928ec77%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20the%20emotional%20hook%20is%20the%20most%20important%20part%20of%20ghostwriting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20usually%20a%20moment%20when%20it's%20obvious%20that%20a%20question%20has%20touched%20a%20nerve%2C%20and%20the%20floodgates%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20advocate%20for%20becoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbara-walters-most-controversial-interviews-from-her-60-year-career-2022-12%5C%