ing%26quot%3B%20and%20resilient%20in%20the%20face%20of%20geopolitical%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20economy%20is%20on%20a%20strong%20wicket%20and%20stable%20footing%20(and)%20demonstrating%20resilience%20in%20the%20face%20of%20geopolitical%20challenges.%20The%20economy%20has%20consolidated%20post-Covid%20recovery%20with%20policymakers%20-%20fiscal%20and%20monetary%20-%20ensuring%20economic%20and%20financial%20stability...%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20pointed%20out%20FY24%20growth%20is%20an%20estimated%208.2%20per%20cent%20with%20the%20economy%20crossing%20the%20eight%20per%20cent%20mark%20in%20three%20of%20four%20quarters%2C%20and%20said%20she%20expects%20momentum%20built%20over%20FY23%20and%20FY24%20to%20be%20carried%20into%20FY25%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20see%20growth%20between%206.5%20and%207%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20%26quot%3Bprospects%20for%20continued%20strong%20growth%20beyond%20FY25%20look%20good...%20subject%20to%20geopolitical%2C%20financial%20market%20and%20climatic%20risks%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20told%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20compared%20favourably%20to%20global%20economic%20growth%20of%203.2%20per%20cent%20in%202023%20(data%20from%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20April).%20%26quot%3BThe%20stark%20difference%20in%20growth%20performance%20of%20countries%20has%20been%20on%20account%20of%20domestic%20structural%20issues%20(and)%20uneven%20exposure%20to%20geopolitical%20conflicts...%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadline%20inflation%20-%20which%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20expects%20at%204.5%20per%20cent%20in%20FY25%20and%204.1%20per%20cent%20the%20following%20year%20-%20is%20%26quot%3Bunder%20control%26quot%3B.%20This%20is%20given%20a%20normal%20monsoon%20and%20no%20external%20or%20policy%20shock%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inflation%20rate%20of%20some%20food%20items%2C%20however%2C%20has%20elevated%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFood%20inflation%2C%20which%20was%206.6%20per%20cent%20in%20FY23%2C%20increased%20to%207.5%20per%20cent%20in%20FY24%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increase%20was%20blamed%20on%20unfavourable%20weather%20conditions%20that%20restricted%20production.%20And%20the%20farmers%20faced%20challenges%20due%20to%20extreme%20weather%20events%20and%20depleted%20reservoirs%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetail%20inflation%2C%20which%20averaged%206.7%20per%20cent%20in%20FY23%2C%20was%20brought%20down%20to%205.4%20per%20cent%20in%20FY24%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20government's%20%26quot%3Btimely%20policy%20interventions%20and%20the%20RBI's%20price%20stability%20measures%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20lowest%20level%20since%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20Economic%20Survey%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Economic%20Survey%20also%20highlighted%20the%20government's%20%26quot%3Bthrust%20on%20capex%20and%20sustained%20momentum%20in%20private%20investment%20has%20boosted%20capital%20formation%20growth...%20by%20nine%20per%20cent%20in%20real%20terms%20in%20FY24%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20fiscal%20balances%2C%20the%20Survey%20said%20%26quot%3Btax%20compliance%20gains%20driven%20by%20procedural%20reforms%2C%20expenditure%20restraint%2C%20and%20increasing%20digitisation%26quot%3B%20had%20helped%20offset%20%26quot%3Bexpansionary%20public%20investment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Current%20Account%20Deficit%2C%20the%20Survey%20said%20it%20stood%20at%200.7%20per%20cent%20of%20GDP%20in%20FY24%2C%20a%20big%20improvement%20from%20the%20deficit%20of%202%20per%20cent%20in%20FY23.%20%26quot%3BExternal%20balance%20has%20been%20pressured%20by%20subdued%20global%20demand%20for%20goods%2C%20but%20strong%20services%20exports%20largely%20counterbalanced%20this...%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bchange%20is%20the%20only%20constant%20for%20a%20country%20with%20high%20growth%20aspirations...%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20for%20high-recovery%20phase%20to%20be%20sustained%20%26quot%3Bthere%20has%20to%20be%20heavy%20lifting%20on%20the%20domestic%20front...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20a%20tricky%20global%20environment%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%2C%20the%20government%20said%2C%20to%20reach%20agreements%20on%20key%20issues%2C%20including%20trade%2C%20investment%2C%20and%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20short-term%20outlook%20is%20positive%20(but)%20the%20long-term%20requires%20a%20clear%20vision%2C%20the%20Economic%20Survey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721638140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fmi87188_union-finance-minister-nirmala-sitharaman_625x300_01_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feconomy-on-strong-wicket-nirmala-sitharaman-presents-economic-survey-6159818%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20tabled%20the%20Economic%20Survey%202023%2F24%20in%20Parliament%20Monday%2C%20a%20day%20before%20she%20will%20present%20a%20record%20seventh%20union%20budget.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feconomy-on-strong-wicket-nirmala-sitharaman-presents-economic-survey-6159818%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feconomy-on-strong-wicket-nirmala-sitharaman-presents-economic-survey-6159818%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feconomy-on-strong-wicket-nirmala-sitharaman-presents-economic-survey-6159818%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anushka%20Ranjan%20on%20friendship%20with%20Vaani-Alia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721637820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111923936%2Cimgsize-32410.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22h