and%20standards%2C%20to%20which%20Justice%20Bhatti%20had%20a%20humorous%20and%20telling%20anecdote.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20one%20vegetarian%20hotel%20run%20by%20a%20Hindu%20and%20one%20by%20a%20Muslim%20in%20Kerala.%20As%20a%20judge%20in%20that%20state%20I%20used%20to%20go%20the%20one%20run%20by%20the%20Muslim.%20He%20had%20international%20standards...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKanwar%20Yatra%20Directive%20Voluntary%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20also%20countered%20authorities'%20insistence%20that%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20directive%20is%20voluntary%2C%20claiming%20UP%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20had%20%26quot%3Bmade%20a%20public%20statement%20that%20the%20directive%20must%20be%20enforced...%20so%20far%20as%20Uttarakhand%2C%20there%20was%20a%20similar%20statement%20(by%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20being%20endorsed%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20in%20both%20UP%20and%20Uttarakhand...%20the%20effect%20is%20that%20employees%20of%20certain%20community%20have%20been%20fired%20after%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petitioners%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20police%20in%20UP's%20Muzaffarnagar%20mandated%20all%20food%20joints%20along%20the%20route%20to%20prominently%20display%20names%20of%20owners.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20being%20done%20to%20ensure%20there%20is%20no%20confusion%20among%20kanwariyas%2C%20and%20no%20allegations%20are%20raised%20in%20the%20future%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20law%20and%20order%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20cops%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20following%20this%20of%20their%20own%20free%20will...%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthree-bjp-allies-question-up-order-to-eateries-during-kanwar-yatra-6155970%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3%20BJP%20Allies%20Qu