0on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F5mvghq7_budget_625x300_22_July_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20will%20be%20presenting%20Modi%203.0's%20first%20budget%20on%20July%2023.%20Already%2C%20there%20has%20been%20much%20debate%20about%20whether%20it%20will%20bring%20anything%20new%20to%20the%20table.%20The%20middle%20class%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20expectations%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20reduction%20of%20taxes%20and%20initiating%20reforms%20to%20simplify%20the%20taxation%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Importance%20Of%20The%20Middle%20Class%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20middle%20class%20constitutes%20around%2031%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%20at%20present%2C%20and%20its%20share%20continues%20to%20rise.%20Notably%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20voters%20from%20this%20section%20have%20supported%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20since%20its%20formation.%20In%20fact%2C%20of%20late%2C%20this%20class%20has%20played%20the%20role%20of%20kingmaker%2C%20providing%20parties%20with%20that%20extra%20push%20to%20cross%20the%20halfway%20mark.%20In%202004%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20when%20the%20turnout%20of%20the%20middle%20class%20had%20declined%20by%2018%25%2C%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20was%20served%20a%20shocking%20defeat.%20%C2%A0In%20the%20recently%20concluded%20general%20election%2C%20as%20much%20as%2035%25%20of%20the%20middle%20class%20backed%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20-%20three%20percentage%20points%20lower%20than%202019.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Congress's%20vote%20share%20among%20this%20class%20increased%20by%20two%20percentage%20points%20since%20the%20last%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Rs.%2010%20lakh%20crore%2C%20the%20middle%20class%20accounts%20for%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20individual%20income%20tax%20collection%20of%20the%20government.%20Also%2C%20not%20more%20than%203%25%20of%20the%20population%20pays%20taxes%20-%20mostly%20comprising%20the%20middle%20class%20-%20and%20it's%20these%20people%20who%20carry%20the%20whole%20of%20the%20tax%20burden%20on%20their%20shoulders.%20The%20value%20of%20personal%20income%20tax%20collected%20is%20more%20than%20corporate%20taxes.%20That%20is%2C%20the%20middle%20class%20is%20paying%20more%20taxes%20than%20all%20corporates%20put%20together%2C%20and%20it's%20this%20class%20the%20government%20relies%20on%20to%20fund%20its%20capex%20and%20welfare%20programmes.%20This%20is%20untenable%20in%20the%20long%20run%20for%20a%20middle-income%20country%20like%20India%20with%20a%20per%20capita%20income%20of%20just%20around%20%242%2C500.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelief%20Long%20Due%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20very%20long%20ago%2C%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202010-11%2C%20corporate%20tax%20collections%20had%20been%20twice%20as%20much%20as%20personal%20income%20tax.%20The%20two%20became%20almost%20equal%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20in%20FY2022-23.%20Since%20then%2C%20personal%20income%20tax%20collections%20have%20been%20budgeted%20to%20be%20higher%20than%20corporate%20taxes.%20But%20while%20the%20corporate%20sector%20was%20given%20a%20big%20tax%20relief%20in%20the%20FY%202019-20%20budget%20with%20a%20tax%20rate%20cut%20from%2030%25%20to%2022%25%2C%20personal%20income%20tax%20has%20seen%20no%20such%20changes%20since%202012-13.%20Deductions%20have%20not%20changed%20for%20years%2C%20and%20haven't%20even%20been%20adjusted%20for%20inflation.%20The%20Centre%20introduced%20a%20new%20tax%20regime%20with%20higher%20slabs%20in%20FY%202020-21%2C%20but%20it%20had%20no%20provisions%20for%20new%20deductions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20middle%20class%20in%20India%20does%20not%20have%20any%20social%20security%2C%20except%20for%20when%20one%20has%20a%20government%20job.%20Most%20education%20and%20health%20facilities%20are%20not%20free%2C%20and%20state-run%20hospitals%20and%20schools%20often%20lack%20quality.%20The%20middle%20class%20is%20getting%20restless%2C%20and%20many%20have%20begun%20questioning%20what%20they%20are%20getting%20in%20return%20for%20the%20hefty%20taxes%20they%20pay.%20Corruption%20and%20freebie%20politics%20have%20only%20exacerbated%20these%20concerns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Tax%20Structure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20tax%20structures%20also%20differ%20from%20other%20countries.%20In%20Singapore%2C%20for%20example%2C%20there%20is%20no%20TDS%20(Tax%20Deducted%20at%20Source)%20on%20salary%20income.%20A%20taxpayer%20get%2012%20months%20after%20the%20assessment%20to%20pay%20taxes.%20Also%2C%20the%20first%2020%2C000%20SGD%20(Rs.%2012.4%20lakh%20at%20the%20current%20exchange%20rate)%20is%20exempt%20from%20taxation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20tax%20slabs.%20The%20highest%20tax%20bracket%20of%2030%25%20in%20India%20kicks%20in%20at%20much%20lower%20incomes.%20In%20China%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20the%2030%25%20tax%20rate%20kicks%20in%20at%204%2C20%2C000%20CNY%2C%20more%20than%20Rs.%2048%20lakh%20as%20per%20the%20current%20exchange%20rate.%20In%20Russia%2C%20all%20income%20is%20taxed%20at%2013%25%2C%20less%20than%20half%20our%20peak%20rate.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20income%20above%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20up%20to%20Rs%2039%20lakh%20is%20taxed%20at%20just%2012%25%20for%20a%20single%20filer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20has%20a%20unique%20situation%20where%20individual%20income%20of%20above%20Rs.%2015%20lakh%20in%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%20and%20above%20Rs.%2010%20lakh%20in%20the%20old%20tax%20regime%20is%20taxed%20at%2030%25.%20Meanwhile%2C%20corporate%20income%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20crores%20is%20subject%20to%20just%2022%25%20tax%2C%20that%20too%20after%20the%20deduction%20of%20expenses.%20Further%2C%20while%20corporates%20are%20taxed%20on%20profit%20(after%20deducting%20expenses%20from%20incomes)%2C%20individuals%20are%20taxed%20on%20income%20(salaries%2C%20professional%20fees%2C%20etc)%2C%20without%20any%20deductions%20available%20for%20expenses%20incurred%20to%20earn%20income%20under%20the%20new%20tax%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoosting%20Consumption%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20consumption%20has%20been%20lagging%2C%20it's%20important%20that%20the%20middle%20class%20is%20encouraged%20to%20unleash%20its%20animal%20spirits.%20Not%20only%20income%20tax%2C%20the%20middle%20class%20is%20a%20big%20contributor%20to%20India's%20GST%20collection%20too%2C%20given%20that%20it%20consumes%20a%20bulk%20of%20the%20goods%20and%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20government%20should%20thus%20keep%20the%20middle%20class%20happy%2C%20especially%20as%20four%20states%20go%20to%20polls%20later%20this%20year.%20This%20class%20expects%20substantial%20relief%2C%20not%20mere%20cosmetic%20changes%20It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20will%20navigate%20this%20tight%20fiscal%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721634660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fi1q8ncuo_budget_625x300_22_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-budget-fy25-meet-the-expectations-of-a-restless-middle-class-6159542%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20middle%20class%20expects%20substantial%20relief%2C%20not%20mere%20cosmetic%20changes%20It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20will%20navigate%20this%20tricky%20fiscal%20challenge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3