pportunity%20to%20raise%20their%20constituency's%20issues%20because%20%26quot%3Bnegative%20politics%26quot%3B%20by%20some%20parties%20had%20wasted%20Parliament's%20time.%20He%20appealed%20to%20MPs%20from%20all%20parties%20to%20set%20aside%20political%20difference%20and%20participate%20in%20constructive%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20the%20Opposition's%20protests%20in%20Parliament%20in%20the%20session%20immediately%20after%20poll%20results%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20there%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutionally%20silence%26quot%3B%20a%20government%20chosen%20by%20the%20people.%20%26quot%3BThere%20cannot%20be%20a%20place%20in%20democratic%20traditions%20for%20attempts%20to%20gag%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20two-and-a-half%20hours%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20remorse%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20referred%20to%20the%20sloganeering%20by%20Opposition%20MPs%20when%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20addressing%20the%20House%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20to%20the%20President's%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20country%20is%20closely%20watching%20and%20hopes%20that%20this%20is%20session%20would%20be%20constructive%2C%20creative%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20to%20fulfil%20their%20dreams.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20important%20milestone%20in%20the%20glorious%20journey%20of%20Indian%20democracy.%20We%20are%20proud%20that%2060%20years%20later%2C%20a%20government%20has%20returned%20to%20power%20for%20the%20third%20time%20and%20is%20going%20to%20present%20its%20first%20budget%20of%20its%20third%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20Union%20Budget%20to%20be%20presented%20tomorrow%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20government%20is%20moving%20forward%20to%20implement%20his%20guarantees.%20%26quot%3BThis%20budget%20is%20an%20important%20budget%20of%20Amrit%20Kaal.%20I