ndian%20team%2C%20the%20selection%20committee%20preferred%20to%20give%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20a%20break%20by%20not%20selecting%20him%20for%20the%20ODI%20series%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Agarkar%20confirmed%20that%20the%20spin-bowling%20all-rounder%20wasn't%20dropped%20from%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20should%20have%20clarified%20this%20when%20we%20announced%20the%20squad.%20He%20hasn't%20been%20dropped%20(but%20rested).%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20Test%20series%20coming%20up%2C%20and%20he%20will%20be%20playing%20a%20lot%20of%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20Agarkar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShubman%20Gill%20As%20Vice-Captain%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20batting%20has%20been%20elevated%20as%20Team%20India's%20vice-captain%20in%20ODIs%20and%20T20Is.%20The%20big%20decision%20comes%20in%20because%20of%20BCCI's%20long-term%20plans%20for%20him.%20Agarkar%20confirmed%20that%20Gill%20is%20a%20player%20in%20all%20three%20formats%20and%20the%20selectors%20want%20to%20give%20him%20ample%20experience%20in%20the%20leadership%20role%2C%20help%20him%20hone%20his%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShubman%20Gill%20is%20the%20guy%20we%20feel%20is%20a%20three-format%20player.%20Has%20shown%20a%20lot%20more%20qualities%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20that's%20what%20we%20hear%20from%20the%20dressing%20room.%20He%20has%20shown%20some%20decent%20leadership%20qualities.%20We%20want%20to%20try%20and%20give%20him%20the%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Agarkar%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHardik%20Pandya's%20Fitness%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20confirming%20that%20Hardik%20is%20still%20an%20extremely%20valuable%20player%20for%20the%20team%2C%20Agarkar%20admitted%20that%20the%20all-rounder's%20fitness%20is%20the%20biggest%20concern%20for%20the%20selectors.%20With%20Hardik%20being%20a%20non-captain%2C%20the%20team%20management%20even%20hopes%20to%20manage%20his%20workload%20and%20skillset%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFitness%20has%20been%20something%20that%20he's%20struggled%20with.%20As%20selectors%2C%20it%20becomes%20difficult%20then.%20The%20thought%20behind%20it%20was%20that%20we%20want%20someone%20(as%20captain)%20who%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20available%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20feel%20we%20can%20manage%20Hardik%20better%2C%20we've%20seen%20what%20he%20can%20do%20with%20the%20bat%20and%20ball%20in%20the%20World%20Cup.%20We%20speak%20to%20every%20player%2C%20about%20whether%20their%20role%20has%20changed.%20And%20yeah%20we've%20spoken%20to%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Shami%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1580-shami-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Shami%3C%2Fa%3E's%20return%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20pacer%20hasn't%20featured%20for%20India%20since%20the%20conclusion%20of%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20last%20year.%20Agarkar%20revealed%20that%20Shami%20has%20resumed%20bowling%20in%20the%20nets%20and%20could%20be%20available%20for%20the%20Bangladesh%20Test%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20started%20to%20bowl.%20The%20first%20Test%20is%2019th%20September.%20That%20was%20always%20the%20goal%20(him%20making%20a%20comeback%20by%20that%20time).%20Whether%20he%20can%20make%20it%20back%20to%20the%20squad%20by%20that%20(Bangladesh%20series)%20time%2C%20I'll%20have%20to%20speak%20with%20the%20guys%20at%20the%20NCA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelationship%20With%20Virat%20Kohli%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20rumour-mill%20over%20Kohli's%20relationship%20with%20Gambhir%20continues%20to%20remain%20a%20big%20talking%20point%2C%20the%20India%20head%20coach%20confirmed%20that%20both%20will%20be%20fighting%20for%20the%20same%20team%2C%20and%20hence%2C%20there's%20no%20question%20of%20their%20perspectives%20being%20divided.%20As%20for%20their%20personal%20relationship%2C%20Gambhir%20refused%20to%20give%20headlines%20for%20TRPs%2C%20saying%20that%20remains%20a%20private%20matter%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20(rumours%20of%20a%20tiff)%20is%20good%20for%20the%20TRP%20but%20my%20relationship%20with%20him%20has%20been%20good.%20What's%20important%20is%20we%20are%20representing%20140%20crore%20Indians.%20We've%20shared%20messages.%20It's%20not%20important%20if%20we%20have%20chatted%20before%20my%20announcement%20or%20after.%20He%20is%20a%20world-class%20player%2C%20I%20have%20huge%20respect%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721634120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fnr57oh0o_gambhir-and-agakar_625x300_22_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsri-lanka-vs-india-2024%2Fgautam-gambhir-press-conference-7-big-revelations-made-by-india-head-coach-and-chief-selector-6159499%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20BCCI%20selection%20committee%20chief%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20buried%20plenty%20of%20rumours%20as%20they%20shed%20light%20on%20some%20gruelling%20topics%20in%20the%20pre-Sri%20Lanka%20tour%20press%20conference.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsri-lanka-vs-india-2024%2Fgautam-gambhir-press-conference-7-big-revelations-made-by-india-head-coach-and-chief-selector-6159499%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsri-lanka-vs-india-2024%2Fgautam-gambhir-press-conference-7-big-revelations-made-by-india-head-coach-and-chief-selector-6159499%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsri-lanka-vs-india-2024%2Fgautam-gambhir-press-conference-7-big-revelations-made-by-india-head-coach-and-chief-selector-6159499%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Celebs%20pay%20last%20respects%20to%20Tishaa%20Kumar%22%2C%22conte