w%2F111921238.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111921238.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fseveral-killed-injured-in-mass-shooting-in-us-mississippi-latest-news%2Farticleshow%2F111921238.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fseveral-killed-injured-in-mass-shooting-in-us-mississippi-latest-news%2Famp_articleshow%2F111921238.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fseveral-killed-injured-in-mass-shooting-in-us-mississippi-latest-news%2Famp_articleshow%2F111921238.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Sudan%2C%20Women%20Forced%20To%20Line%20Up%20For%20Sex%20With%20Soldiers%20For%20Food%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20war-torn%20Sudan%2C%20women%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20soldiers%20to%20get%20food%20to%20feed%20their%20families%2C%20a%20report%20by%20The%20Guardian%20said.%20Over%20two%20dozen%20women%20who%20fled%20the%20Sudanese%20city%20of%20Omdurman%20said%20that%20having%20sex%20with%20soldiers%20was%20the%20only%20way%20they%20could%20access%20food%20or%20goods%20that%20they%20could%20sell%20to%20raise%20money%20to%20feed%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%20who%20spoke%20to%20the%20Guardian%20said%20the%20assaults%20took%20place%20in%20factories%20across%20the%20the%20city%20where%20the%20food%20is%20stockpiled.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20of%20my%20parents%20are%20too%20old%20and%20sick%20and%20I%20never%20let%20my%20daughter%20go%20out%20to%20look%20for%20food.%20I%20went%20to%20the%20soldiers%20and%20that%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20get%20food%20%E2%80%93%20they%20were%20everywhere%20in%20the%20factories%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20woman%2C%20who%20was%20forced%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20soldiers%20at%20a%20meat-processing%20factory%20in%20May%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assaults%20reportedly%20began%20soon%20after%20a%20civil%20war%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20country%20which%20has%20seen%20the%20country's%20army%20face%20off%20against%20paramilitary%20Rapid%20Support%20Forces.%20Reports%20of%20rape%20by%20armed%20men%20emerged%20within%20days%20of%20the%20conflict%20starting%20on%2015%20April%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20Sudan%20has%20killed%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%2C%20with%20some%20estimates%20placing%20the%20death%20count%20as%20high%20as%20150%2C000.%20The%20war%20has%20created%20the%20world's%20worst%20displacement%20crisis%20--%20with%20more%20than%2011%20million%20uprooted%20and%20brought%20the%20country%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20famine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20women%20have%20come%20forward%20sharing%20harrowing%20tales%20of%20RSF%20fighters%20sexually%20abusing%20them%20in%20a%20systematic%20manner%20in%20areas%20under%20their%20control.%20The%20soldiers%20have%20also%20demanded%20sex%20in%20exchange%20for%20access%20to%20abandoned%20houses%20where%20it%20is%20still%20possible%20to%20loot%20items%20to%20sell%20in%20local%20markets%2C%20the%20women%20told%20the%20Guardian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%20said%20that%20she%20was%20allowed%20to%20take%20food%2C%20kitchen%20equipment%20and%20perfumes%20from%20empty%20houses%20after%20she%20had%20sex%20with%20soldiers.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20went%20through%20is%20indescribable%2C%20I%20would%20not%20wish%20it%20on%20an%20enemy%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20only%20did%20it%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20feed%20my%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20of%20the%20city%20claimed%20they%20see%20soldiers%20bringing%20women%20to%20abandoned%20houses%20where%20they%20were%20made%20to%20queue%20up%20as%20soldier%20picked%20th