against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Centre%20citing%20a%20report%20by%20IIT%20Madras%20director%2C%20Professor%20V%20Kamakoti%2C%20to%20stress%20that%20there%20was%20no%20malpractice%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20all-India%20exam%20for%20admission%20to%20MBBS%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarendra%20Hooda%2C%20the%20counsel%20for%20the%20petitioner%20in%20the%20NEET%20UG%20case%2C%20had%20said%20the%20data%20analytics%20report%20was%20not%20reliable%20and%20alleged%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%20because%20the%20IIT%20Madras%20director%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20NTA%20governing%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERefuting%20this%2C%20NTA%20has%20said%20in%20a%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20that%20the%20director%20of%20an%20IIT%20that%20conducts%20the%20JEE%20(Advanced)%20exam%20for%20engineering%20aspirants%20is%20an%20ex-officio%20member%20of%20the%20NTA%20governing%20body%20and%20this%20year%2C%20IIT%20Madras%20conducted%20the%20exam.%20However%2C%20the%20core%20work%20of%20NTA%20is%20handled%20by%20its%20managing%20committee.%20The%20governing%20body%2C%20it%20said%2C%20only%20looks%20at%20policy%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IIT%20Madras%20director%2C%20the%20NTA%20said%2C%20had%20nominated%20another%20professor%20to%20attend%20the%20governing%20body's%20meetings.%20And%20this%20professor%2C%20too%2C%20had%20not%20attended%20any%20meeting%20since%20December%20last%20year.%20The%20IIT%20Madras%20director%2C%20it%20said%2C%20had%20not%20attended%20any%20meeting%20of%20NTA%20governing%20body%20since%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20hearing%20into%20the%20case%20of%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20NEET%2C%20which%20has%20sparked%20nationwide%20protests%2C%20the%20Centre%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20data%20analytics%20of%20results%20shows%20that%20the%20marks%20distribution%20follows%20the%20bell-shaped%20curve%20that%20is%20witnessed%20in%20any%20large-scale%20examination%20and%20there%20is%20no%20indication%20of%20an%20ab