arolina)%2C%20along%20with%20Gavin%20Newsom%20(California)%2C%20JD%20Pritzker%20(Illinois)%2C%20Andy%20Beshear%20(Kentucky)%2C%20and%20Transportation%20Secretary%20Pete%20Buttigieg.%20Arizona%20Senator%20Mark%20Kelly%20is%20also%20a%20notable%20contender.%20Speculative%20suggestions%20like%20Hillary%20Clinton%2C%20Michelle%20Obama%2C%20and%20Oprah%20Winfrey%20are%20deemed%20unlikely.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Chidanand%20Rajghatta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flotus-to-potus-focus-shifting-the-kamalas-running-mate%2Farticleshow%2F111914875.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flotus-to-potus-focus-shifting-the-kamalas-running-mate%2Famp_articleshow%2F111914875.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flotus-to-potus-focus-shifting-the-kamalas-running-mate%2Famp_articleshow%2F111914875.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Economic%20Survey%20To%20Be%20Tabled%20In%20Parliament%20Today.%20What%20Is%20it%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20is%20set%20to%20present%20the%20Economic%20Survey%202023-24%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20Parliament%20today.%20Union%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20will%20table%20the%20pre-budget%20document%20in%20Parliament%2C%20a%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20full%20Budget%20presentation%20for%202024-25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Economic%20Survey%202023-24%20will%20be%20presented%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20at%201%20pm%20and%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20at%202%20pm%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20press%20conference%20by%20Chief%20Economic%20Adviser%20Anantha%20Nageswaran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20Budget%20will%20be%20keenly%20watched%20as%20several%20major%20economies%20in%20the%20world%20have%20been%20struggling.%20India%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20retained%20its%20tag%20as%20the%20fastest-growing%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20an%20Economic%20Survey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Economic%20Survey%20document%2C%20prepared%20by%20the%20Economic%20Division%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Economic%20Affairs%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20and%20formulated%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20the%20chief%20economic%20adviser%2C%20will%20give%20insights%20into%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20various%20indicators%20of%202023-24%20(April-March)%20and%20some%20outlook%20for%20the%20current%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20report%20card%20on%20the%20economy%20and%20presents%20the%20growth%20outlook.%20The%20survey%20gives%20a%20detailed%20account%20of%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20prospects%20and%20policy%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Economic%20Survey%20provides%20statistical%20information%20and%20analysis%20on%20various%20sectors%20of%20the%20economy%20as%20well%20as%20data%20on%20employment%2C%20GDP%20growth%2C%20inflation%2C%20and%20the%20budget%20deficit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistory%20of%20Economic%20Survey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20economic%20survey%20reportedly%20came%20into%20existence%20in%201950-51%2C%20when%20it%20used%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20budget%20documents.%20In%20the%201960s%2C%20it%20was%20separated%20from%20the%20Budget%20documents%20and%20presented%20the%20day%20before%20the%20Union%20Budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20feature%20that%20many%20will%20look%20out%20for%20is%20its%20central%20theme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20central%20theme%20was%20'Agile%20Approach'%2C%20which%20emphasized%20on%20India's%20economic%20response%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20shock.%20In%202023%2C%20it%20was%20'recovery%20complete'%2C%20when%20the%20economy%20staged%20a%20broad-based%20recovery%20from%20pandemic-induced%20contraction%2C%20Russian-Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20and%20inflation%2C%20and%20ascended%20to%20the%20pre-pandemic%20growth%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20along%20with%20the%20sectoral%20chapters%2C%20the%20Survey%20document%20also%20adds%20new%20need-based%20chapters%20that%20need%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20eyes%20will%20be%20on%20the%20major%20announcements%20made%20by%20the%20finance%20minister%20and%20the%20government's%20forward-looking%20guidance%20about%20the%20overall%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20upcoming%20budget%20presentation%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20will%20surpass%20the%20record%20set%20by%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Morarji%20Desai%2C%20who%20presented%20five%20annual%20budgets%20and%20one%20interim%20budget%20between%201959%20and%201964%20as%20finance%20minister.%20Sitharaman's%20upcoming%20budget%20speech%20will%20be%20her%20seventh.%20Sitharaman%20has%20surpassed%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20Arun%20Jaitley%2C%20P.%20Chidambaram%2C%20and%20Yashwant%20Sinha%2C%20who%20each%20presented%20five%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721618940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2fc1sh3g_nirmala-sitharaman_650x400_02_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funion-budget-2024-economic-survey-to-be-tabled-in-parliament-today-what-is-it-6158554%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government%20is%20set%20to%20present%20the%20Economic%20Survey%202023-24%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20Parliament%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funion-budget-2024-economic-survey-to-be-tabled-in-parliament-today-what-is-it-6158554%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funion-budget-2024-economic-survey-to-be-tabled-in-parliament-today-what-is-it-6158554%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funion-budget-2024-economic-survey-to-be-