20in%2C%20and%20any%20guidance%20required%20in%20the%20case.%20This%20has%20helped%20give%20a%20human%20touch%20and%20make%20online%20proceedings%20easier%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20working%20online%20also%20poses%20challenges%20such%20as%20contactability%20with%20parties%20who%20have%20old%20phone%20numbers%20registered%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20support%20from%20lawyers%20who%20do%20not%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20ODR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20started%20sending%20offline%20notices%20to%20parties%20and%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20experience%20for%20our%203%2C000%20lawyers%20is%20good%20so%20that%20they%20can%20spread%20the%20word%20about%20ODR.%20We%20are%20also%20experimenting%20with%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20handle%20more%20case%20volume%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sama%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20season%203%20and%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%20%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357646%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESama%20was%20recently%20featured%20in%20the%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20season%203%20and%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20speedy%20out%20of%20court%20settlements%2C%20Sama%20incentivises%20success%20rates%20of%20cases%20instead%20of%20paying%20fee%20per%20hearing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20we%20see%20that%20lawyers%20try%20to%20extract%20more%20amounts%20from%20clients%20and%20keep%20delaying%20the%20case.%20But%20our%20business%20model%20is%20based%20on%20incentivising%20the%20lawyers%20based%20on%20the%20success%20rates%20of%20the%20cases.%20We%20give%204x%20money%20if%20the%20settlement%20is%20reached%20on%20time.%20This%20encourages%20mediators%20to%20solve%20the%20cases%20fast%20and%20reach%20a%20conclusion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20case%2C%20Sama%20charges%20one%20percent%20of%20the%20claim%20amounts%20in%20the%20case.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20dispute%20is%20within%20a%C2%A0%20lakh%2C%20we%20charge%20the%20client%20Rs%201%2C000%2C%20whereas%20we%20take%20Rs%202%2C000%20for%20clients%20between%20Rs%201-3%20lakh.%20This%20is%2099%20percent%20cheaper%20than%20the%20courts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20this%20year%2C%20Sama%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20season%203%20and%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20from%20boAt%20co-founder%20Aman%20Gupta%2C%20Namita%20Thapar%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Emcure%20Pharmaceuticals%2C%20and%20Ritesh%20Agarwal%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20OYO%20Rooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20did%20we%20receive%20the%20funding%20but%20this%20exposure%20also%20helped%20us%20get%20a%20good%20reach%20and%20spread%20awareness%20about%20ODR.%20Our%20idea%20got%20a%20validation%20when%20we%20explained%20it%20to%20the%20viewers%20in%20a%20non-legal%20language.%20Finally%2C%20our%20families%20also%20understood%20what%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20success%20of%20the%20startup%2C%20Pranjal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPersonally%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20very%20challenging%20but%20rewarding%20journey%20for%20us.%20I%20really%20feel%20Sama%20is%20a%20divine%20%3Cem%3Esewa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(service).%20Every%20day%2C%20we%20deal%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20negativity%20but%20when%20years%20long%20disputes%20are%20solved%2C%20we%20get%20equal%20amounts%20of%20satisfaction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20take%20us%20another%2010%20years%20to%20make%20Sama%20a%20primary%20resort%20for%20civil%20disputes%20to%20be%20able%20to%20reduce%20the%20burden%20on%20courts%20so%20that%20they%20can%20focus%20on%20criminal%20cases%20instead%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Pranjal%20Sinha.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721390593000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-2-1721374464.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D357644%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pranjal%20Sinha%2C%20Akshetha%20Ashok%2C%20and%20Vikram%20Kumar%20started%20Sama%2C%20a%20legal%20startup%20working%20to%20reduce%20court%20load%20with%20fast%20and%20cost-effective%20resolution%20of%20civil%20disputes%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357644%2Fsama-legal-tech-startup-resolves-civil-disputes-through-online-dispute-resolution-odr%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Unexpected%20Origin%20Stories%20of%20Chicken%20Tikka%20Masala%20%26amp%3B%20a%20Must-Try%20Recipe%20by%20Chef%20Ranveer%20Brar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%E2%80%99s%20on%20their%20early%20morning%20jog%20or%20a%20drive%20in%20South%20Manchester%2C%20England%20has%20more%20often%20than%20not%20had%20the%20feeling%20of%20having%20just%20been%20swallowed%20up%20by%20