tretch%20and%20the%20development%20of%20ancillary%20ponds%20and%20check%20dams%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20near%20extinction%2C%20the%20river%20now%20flourishes.%20This%20has%20significantly%20mitigated%20the%20incidence%20of%20waterborne%20diseases%20and%20provided%20reliable%20water%20sources%20for%20irrigation%20and%20domestic%20use%20in%2039%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20also%20integrated%20water-soak%20pits%20around%206%2C000%20handpumps%20to%20ensure%20that%20excess%20water%20filters%20into%20the%20ground%2C%20substantially%20reducing%20surface%20runoff%20and%20promoting%20groundwater%20recharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-2-1721270285.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Himanshu%20credits%20the%20success%20of%20the%20project%20to%20NREGA%20workers%20and%20collaborative%20efforts%20of%20gram%20panchayats%20in%20Varanasi.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-2-1721270285.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-2-1721270285-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-2-1721270285-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-2-1721270285-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-2-1721270285-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357473%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHimanshu%20credits%20the%20success%20of%20the%20project%20to%20NREGA%20workers%20and%20the%20collaborative%20efforts%20of%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Varanasi.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanshu%20also%20collaborated%20with%20the%20World%20Wildlife%20Fund%20and%20top%20educational%20institutes%20such%20IIT%20(Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology)-BHU%20(Banaras%20Hindu%20Universiry)%20to%20provide%20topographical%20and%20environmental%20insights%20on%20the%20wetlands%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20to%20know%20that%20if%20we%20dig%20out%20the%20wetlands%20in%20a%20scientific%20manner%2C%20they%20will%20be%20filled%20with%20water%20throughout%20the%20year%20and%20recharge%20groundwater%20and%20supply%20water%20to%20nearby%20rural%20development%20blocks%20and%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20will%20take%20us%20three%20more%20months%20to%20complete%20this%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Himanshu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20multi-pronged%20approach%2C%20Himanshu%20says%20the%20water%20table%20in%20the%20region%20has%20improved.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20our%20water%20table%20has%20increased%20from%200.8%20to%201%20metre.%20One%20of%20the%20blocks%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20Pindra%2C%20has%20come%20out%20of%20the%20dark%20status%2C%20which%20is%20given%20to%20a%20block%20with%20extremely%20poor%20groundwater%20levels.%20In%20Pindra%2C%20water%20had%20reduced%20to%20an%20extent%20that%20we%20had%20to%20ban%20any%20kind%20of%20groundwater%20extraction.%20There%2C%20we%20have%20observed%20an%20increase%20of%201.7%20metres%20in%20the%20water%20table%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20revival%20of%20the%20Nad%20river%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20holistic%20approach%20towards%20groundwater%20recharge%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20estimates%20to%20have%20spent%20Rs%2080%20crore%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20He%20urges%20citizens%20to%20be%20cognisant%20of%20the%20water%20scarcity%20in%20the%20country%20and%2