f%20Industrious%20Communities%2C%20or%20the%20EPIC%20Opportunity.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20age%20creed%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202022%20story%2C%20%3Cem%3EForbes%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20owners%20of%20small%20home%20businesses%20the%20%E2%80%98OG%20entrepreneurs%E2%80%99.%20The%20moniker%20is%20backed%20by%20statistics.%20According%20to%20a%202024%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EPraxis%20Global%20Alliance%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20Enmasse%20World%2C%20in%20FY%202023%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20247%20million%20entrepreneurial%20households%20drove%20an%20%248.8%20trillion%20transaction%20value%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20significant%20portion%20being%20informal%20transactions%2C%20unleashing%20a%20new%20economic%20landscape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20in%20home-owned%20businesses%20and%20their%20success%20are%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20notion%20that%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economic%20prospects%20do%20not%20necessarily%20lie%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20commercial%20enterprises.%20But%20rather%2C%20that%20magic%20can%20often%20be%20brewed%20in%20the%20smallest%20of%20farms%20and%20home%20kitchens.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20India%E2%80%99s%20collective%20growth%20story%20is%20unfolding%2C%20every%20single%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Frural-startups-1-1720763650.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yogesh%20Gawande%E2%80%99s%20Niyo-Farm%20Tech%20crafts%20innovative%20agri-equipment%20for%20farmers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Frural-startups-1-1720763650.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Frural-startups-1-1720763650-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fe